      <title>华盛顿地区人工智能就业岗位随着联邦机构拥抱新技术而激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/washington-area-enjoys-ai-job-surge-as-feds-embrace-new-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新研究表明，随着政府及其承包商拥抱新兴技术，美国首都正在抢占大量需要人工智能技能的新工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/washington-area-enjoys-ai-job-surge-as-feds-embrace-new-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta 耗资 8 亿美元在印第安纳州建造新的人工智能数据中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/meta-building-new-800-million-ai-focused-data-center-in-indiana</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 正在印第安纳州建设一座耗资 8 亿美元的数据中心，该数据中心将进行优化以处理人工智能服务，这标志着 Facebook 母公司为获得新技术优势而做出的最新尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/meta-building-new-800-million-ai-focused-data-center-in-indiana</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 15:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tinder 要求哥伦比亚用户在致命吸毒后审查匹配对象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/tinder-tells-colombia-users-to-vet-matches-after-fatal-druggings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tinder 向哥伦比亚用户发出安全警告，因为越来越多的犯罪分子使用这款流行的约会应用来引诱受害者下毒和抢劫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/tinder-tells-colombia-users-to-vet-matches-after-fatal-druggings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 15:12:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软在游戏领域裁员 1,900 人，其中包括动视暴雪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/microsoft-cuts-1-900-jobs-in-gaming-including-at-activision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司将在其视频游戏部门裁员 1,900 人，其中包括动视暴雪公司，该公司在去年底完成的收购中以 690 亿美元收购了该部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/microsoft-cuts-1-900-jobs-in-gaming-including-at-activision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 14:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利亿万富翁马特家族竞购竞争对手银行，押注银行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/billionaire-clan-bets-on-chile-banking-with-bid-for-rival-lender-grupo-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利亿万富翁马特家族在林业、发电和电信领域拥有资产，正寻求通过与当地竞争对手合并其银行业务来扩大其在金融服务领域的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/billionaire-clan-bets-on-chile-banking-with-bid-for-rival-lender-grupo-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 14:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着安全争论的持续，Meta 收紧了青少年信息设置</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/meta-tightens-teen-message-settings-as-safety-debate-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着担心有害内容的立法者和家长继续向社交媒体平台施压，Meta Platforms Inc. 正在加强 Instagram 和 Facebook 上针对青少年的默认直接消息设置，以加强安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/meta-tightens-teen-message-settings-as-safety-debate-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 13:16:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PayPal首席执行官承诺“震惊”，分析师和交易员意见不一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/paypal-has-analysts-and-traders-divided-as-ceo-promises-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师们纷纷认输，而一些投资者则在 PayPal Holdings Inc. 周四举行的一场活动之前为该公司的股票上涨做准备，预计该公司将在该活动中展示其创新技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/paypal-has-analysts-and-traders-divided-as-ceo-promises-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 12:52:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管订户流失，康卡斯特仍实现盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/comcast-earnings-top-forecasts-while-cable-losses-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[康卡斯特公司(Comcast Corp.)公布的盈利超出华尔街预期后，股价创下六个月来最大涨幅。尽管这家美国有线电视巨头的订户数量持续下降，但情况仍然如此。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/comcast-earnings-top-forecasts-while-cable-losses-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 12:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
